Hi Andrew,
We have heard from other Volks that the center section can be broken even 
with a 1600cc engine with the right amount of RPMing the engine way up and poping 
the clutch.
You might want to install a Rhino brand tranny center section.  Those are 
much thicker casted for better strength.
